{"tid":2137853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華爾街日報: 蘋果面臨中國AI公司14億美元的Siri專利訴訟","createTime":"2020-08-03T08:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T11:19:49.000Z","uid":185631,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4defc2002026e35932e37fa5bbadc0b4db790a5b","tid":2137853,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:43:08.000Z","msg":"蘋果正面臨一項專利訴訟，該訴訟有可能阻止其在中國銷售許多產品<br />\n<br />\n一家人工智能公司最近為類似於蘋果Siri的語音助手授予了中國專利，該公司已針對蘋果提起了專利侵權訴訟，如果訴訟成功，這可能會阻止這家美國科技巨頭在全球第二大經濟體中出售其許多產品。<br />\n<br />\n美國東部時間2020年8月3日凌晨2:27，一家人工智能公司最近為與蘋果公司類似的語音助手授予了中國專利。Siri已針對蘋果提起專利侵權訴訟，如果訴訟成功，則可以阻止這家美國科技巨頭在全球第二大經濟體中銷售其許多產品。<br />\n<br />\n上海知真網絡技術有限公司週一在一份聲明中表示，正在上海法院起訴蘋果，要求其賠償人民幣100億元（約合14.3億美元）的損失，指控iPhone和iPad製造商的產品受到侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/apple-faces-1-4-billion-lawsuit-by-chinese-ai-firm-in-siri-patent-fight-11596436018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fapple-faces-1-4-billion-lawsuit-by-chinese-ai-firm-in-siri-patent-fight-11596436018&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F5Khd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=d8bc2a2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/apple-faces-1-4-billion-lawsuit-by-chinese-ai-firm-in-siri-patent-fight-11596436018</a>"},{"pid":"234cfc4cb383dea236068d05c8b970ef7cead468","tid":2137853,"uid":194326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:45:47.000Z","msg":"Jordon都係抄喬丹"},{"pid":"fffb83d4636f8fce8267bea53961d59a71984e09","tid":2137853,"uid":143727,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:48:34.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔撚明，又冇故事背景，講野一舊舊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0分重作"},{"pid":"84d5c97bc9b35b9b0c053754db2a700f4909548d","tid":2137853,"uid":18660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"Siri已針對蘋果提起專利侵權訴訟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im